README.md:50:> **The headline exhibit, machine-checked in CI:** `fixtures/ucp-conformance-ci/valid/conformant-but-false.json` **passes** official-schema conformance and **fails** the truth leg on a price lie. Shape-valid is not true. *(CI = the real thing, not a figure of speech: [`.github/workflows/ci.yml`](.github/workflows/ci.yml) runs `npm run verify` — which includes this differential — plus the legacy suite on every push and PR; first green run observed 2026-07-11 (run 29133350771), most recent observed green 2026-07-12 (run 29208347657 on `d6c7a4d`).)*
