docs/reviews/codex-2026-07-08-deploy-slice-raw-pass1.md:2408:2. **No P1/P2 correctness issue found in `output: "export"` itself.** Current app evidence fits Next static export constraints: `app/merchant/[id]/page.tsx` has `generateStaticParams()`, no `next/image`, no app route handlers, no `cookies`/`headers`/Server Actions/rewrites/redirects in `next.config.ts`. Next’s current static export docs confirm `output: 'export'` emits `out/`, supports Server Components at build time, and rejects features needing runtime server logic. Source: https://nextjs.org/docs/app/guides/static-exports
