   821	        <p class="site-end">Design-lane sample &mdash; &ldquo;Split Stage&rdquo; (Variation C, 2026-07-12). Not served by the live site; a design-process record for owner reaction. Brief: docs/design-brief-s6b-2026-07-11.md.</p>
