   616	  <!-- ============================== #honesty ============================== -->
   617	  <section id="honesty" aria-labelledby="honesty-h2">
   618	    <div class="sec-inner">
   619	      <div class="sec-head reveal">
   620	        <p class="eyebrow"><svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#ic-person"/></svg> What this is &mdash; and what it is not</p>
   621	        <h2 class="h2" id="honesty-h2">A simulated prototype, honest about its own edges.</h2>
   622	        <p class="prose">The restaurant, its menu, and its records are invented; the verification rules, the pinned data-format standard, and the codified fee caps are real. The site is a static replay of committed fixtures &mdash; it initiates nothing. This project began as a merchant activation prototype; that first product is preserved, working, as the legacy activation module.</p>
   623	      </div>
